<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="O" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Oershade" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">O'ershade,</orth> to make dark and gloomy: <cit><quote>fear --s me,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wt 1.2.457" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. I, 2, 457</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>dark cloudy death --s his beams of life,</quote> <bibl n="shak. 3h6 2.6.62" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C II, 6, 62</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>black night o. thy day,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r3 1.2.131" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 2, 131</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>